## Test Case 5:
## - recursive WITH Query: Optimization on query with outside filter. 
##   Predicate pushdown optimization on recursive iterations  value
##                         4) depth between 3 and 5
##   Pushdown optimization should be reflected for recursive branch
## =======================================================================
explain basic
WITH rw (head, depth, empno, mgr, cum_cost, path ) AS
( 
     SELECT empno, 1, empno, mgr, sal, concat(empno)
